      "title": "Ranil takes oaths as Acting President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as the Acting President in the presence of Chief Justice Jayantha Jayasuriya.",
        "Wickremesinghe was appointed as the Acting President, following the resignation of Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Parliament to meet on 20th July to elect new President; Nominations on 19th July"
